<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>53</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 suī rán jiàn bù dào yuè guāng, suī rán jiàn bù dào tài yáng,
 dàn zhǔ shì wǒ men xīn zhōng yǒng bù miè de guāng!
 zài tā de guāng zhōng mò xiǎng, zài tā de guāng zhōng gē chàng,
 tā de ài guǎng wú yá yuán yuǎn liú zhǎng,
 xīn bèi ēn gǎn, tóng shēng sòng yáng,
 dé shèng de shì wǒ men de zhǔ, wàn wáng zhī wáng!
 dé shèng de shì wǒ men de zhǔ, wàn wáng zhī wáng!</lyrics>
<title>suī rán jiàn bù dào yuè guāng 迦南53</title>
</song>